  <div class="flex items-center font-primary flex-col">
    <h1 class="text-4xl">About</h1>
    <p class="mx-60 mt-5 mb-5 text-2xl">
      Open Labs Nepal is an open-source platform built to empower students
      across Nepal by fostering a culture of collaboration, knowledge sharing,
      and academic support. Designed with simplicity and accessibility in mind,
      it serves as a central hub where students from various universities and
      colleges can explore and contribute lab work related to their academic
      courses.
    </p>
