      are open, accessible, and shaped by collaboration.
    </p>
    <p class="text-xl">Open Labs Nepal enables students to:</p>
    <ul class="text-xl list-disc">
      <li>
        Browse and access lab work submitted by peers from different
        universities, colleges, and courses.
      </li>
      <li>
        Contribute their own lab work and make it available to the wider
        academic community.
      </li>
      <li>
        Engage with others through a shared commitment to openness and
        educational growth.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
